Recommends: mpd (>= 0.16~), python-mpd (>= 0.3~)
Description: OSD lyrics display for various media players
 OSD Lyrics is a lyrics display program, inspired by lrcdis. It supports
 communication with music players via mpd, mpris (v1 and v2), and its own
 HTTP API.
 .
 OSD Lyrics can download lyrics from following web sites:
 * viewlyrics.com
 * xiami.com
